<p><strong><a href="/ningen-no-sato-ambrose">欢迎来到安布罗斯餐厅幻想乡人类村落分店！</a></strong><br />
+<strong><tt>141</tt></strong><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;</span><sup>&#8230;</sup> <strong><tt>81</tt></strong><br />
