<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/forum/t-13173483/view-of-art#post-4561918">关于“艺术”的定义和“是否应该给他人看到才算是“艺术”的思考</a></p>
</div>
<div id="wiki-tab-0-6" style="display:none">
<p>什么？居然还有留言板？直接点下面的编辑就可以留言了——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yuannn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6062512); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6062512&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="YUANNN" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6062512)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yuannn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6062512); return false;">YUANNN</a></span></p>
<p>不愧是莳椛，人事都是带艺家）顺祝学/画业有成——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mo-ring" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3606007); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3606007&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="Mo-ring" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3606007)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mo-ring" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3606007); return false;">Mo-ring</a></span></p>
<p>网络千里来相会，互相偷菜传真情。——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shineshadowd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3967806); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3967806&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="ShineShadowD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3967806)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shineshadowd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3967806); return false;">ShineShadowD</a></span></p>
<p>辣么可爱的阿园一定很好吃！——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yixi-windbell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5867553); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5867553&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="yixi_Windbell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5867553)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yixi-windbell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5867553); return false;">yixi_Windbell</a></span></p>
<p>我好爱阿园的话，根本不后悔和阿园认识！（是我的荣幸啊），以后可以的话我会给你做白切鸡的！——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yuexuan" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5299777); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5299777&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="YUEXUAN" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5299777)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yuexuan" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5299777); return false;">YUEXUAN</a></span></p>
<p>阿园好可爱！五毛一条，括号删除 ——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pokm" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662223); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3662223&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="pokm" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3662223)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pokm" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662223); return false;">pokm</a></span></p>
<p>我 优先地记住 留言的技术 有钱的秘书 给我 悠闲地记录着 我的 出场 费<br />
数好我的押韵 数量 我不想 阻挡 你们的 目光 不妨偶尔出现一次<br />
我也希望国足有一天能出线 一次 不过是这个意思 其他都是其次<br />
你的 观点 可能是这和留言没有 关联 关键 是记得给我点个三连<br />
——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/purples0ul-ding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2334417); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2334417&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="PurpleS0ul_Ding" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2334417)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/purples0ul-ding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2334417); return false;">PurpleS0ul_Ding</a></span></p>
<p>艺 作 魔 改 小 能 手(不愧是你) ——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fishsimple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6116085); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6116085&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="FishSimple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6116085)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fishsimple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6116085); return false;">FishSimple</a></span></p>
<p>确实，私认为阿园才是中分的小清新<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">和可爱</span>代表。真的很不错。<br />
——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sciencekiller" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5480202); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5480202&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="sciencekiller" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5480202)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sciencekiller" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5480202); return false;">sciencekiller</a></span></p>
<p>好可爱，想揉（ ——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zzzzzac" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5215451); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5215451&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="ZZZZZac" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5215451)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zzzzzac" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5215451); return false;">ZZZZZac</a></span></p>
<p>回复<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/purples0ul-ding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2334417); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2334417&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="PurpleS0ul_Ding" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2334417)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/purples0ul-ding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2334417); return false;">PurpleS0ul_Ding</a></span>：三连是不可能的，是永远也不可能的（bushi——已经神隐了的用户</p>
<p>吹爆阿园老师！不过阿园对白切鸡有什么怨念嘛，还是说看不起咱盐水鸭？（狗头——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/auroriaaaaa" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5474061); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5474061&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="Auroriaaaaa" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5474061)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/auroriaaaaa" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5474061); return false;">Auroriaaaaa</a></span></p>
<p>园哥太神了!这么好的园哥你值得拥有！<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">不要998也不要98，一只白切鸡即可带回家</span>对不起跑错片场了。——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yuuuutsu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5949529); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5949529&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="Yuuuutsu" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5949529)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yuuuutsu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5949529); return false;">Yuuuutsu</a></span></p>
<p>看看人家可爱的阿园，我什么时候才能把自己的艺作页和人事页咕完<br />
——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/frozen-starry-sky" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6114202); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6114202&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="Frozen starry sky" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6114202)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/frozen-starry-sky" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6114202); return false;">Frozen starry sky</a></span></p>
<p>园园圆圆杀杀分不清楚（）——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sciencekiller" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5480202); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5480202&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="sciencekiller" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5480202)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sciencekiller" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5480202); return false;">sciencekiller</a></span></p>
<p>我叫夹克，夹克，夹克，不叫杰克，阿园不准故意叫错（震声——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacketjiong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6151941); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6151941&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="JacKeTJioNG" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6151941)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacketjiong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6151941); return false;">JacKeTJioNG</a></span></p>
<p>是哪个yuan来着（圆/园？）要不要试试烤鸭）——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smith-sister-con" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4381648); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4381648&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="Smith_sister-con" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4381648)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smith-sister-con" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4381648); return false;">Smith_sister-con</a></span></p>
<p>给阿园倒一杯卡布奇诺（）——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brucewu0463" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5526785); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5526785&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610099309" alt="BruceWu0463" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5526785)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brucewu0463" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5526785); return false;">BruceWu0463</a></span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
